The Story

Meet Muqiet the founder of Coach.ID or affectionately known as Coach Muqiet. Graduating from the prestigious University of Indonesia, Muqiet blazed a trail of success, becoming one of the youngest CEOs in the nation when he founded his private company at the young age of 20. His visionary mindset and innovative ideas caught the attention of national news outlets, propelling him into the limelight as an inspiring entrepreneur, setting the trend for green weddings in the beautiful archipelago of Indonesia.

In 2010, Coach Muqiet embarked on a noble mission to unlock the untapped potential within others, empowering them to become the best versions of themselves. LinkedIn recognized his expertise and invited him to join their esteemed career community, where he has been assisting people worldwide with personalized guidance to conquer their challenges. Moreover, donning the mantle of a Certified Digital Marketer and Data Protection Expert, he now stands at the forefront of transforming global professionals and businesses, leveraging his extensive 12-year digital marketing experience and stellar certifications.

Esteemed public figures such as Mr. Hamdan Zoelva and Abah Ihsan Baihaqi have sought his help on personal branding strategies amidst the ever-evolving digital era. Hailing from the enchanting island of Bali and currently residing in Jakarta - Indonesia, Coach Muqiet's legacy continues to unfold through his pioneering agency, Markethink, leaving an indelible mark on the world of entrepreneurship and digital innovation.
